	13.1 Ubuntu Software Center: Compiz Fusion Icon
14. Jdownloader
	14.1 In terminal:
		sudo add-apt-repository ppa:jd-team/jdownloader
		sudo apt-get update
		sudo apt-get install jdownloader
	14.2 Application -> Internet -> JDownloader (click and wait...)
	14.3 Download a new icon from http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?t=1475761
	14.4 Go to /home/zexi/.jdownloader/jd/img/logo, copy the downloaded icon here. This will make the tray icon looks transparent.
15. Sensors
	15.1 In terminal:
		sudo apt-get install lm-sensors
		sudo apt-get install hddtemp
		sudo sensors-detect
		(all "yes")
	15.2 restart computer, then go to terminal:
		sensors
		sudo apt-get install sensors-applet
	15.3 Right-clicking on the desktop panel, selecting “Add to Panel,” Add “Hardware Sensors Monitor”.
